x10.matrix.sparse

Class SymSparseCSC

  • x10.matrix.Matrix
    • x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSC
      • x10.matrix.sparse.SymSparseCSC

  • public class SymSparseCSC
extends SparseCSC
    Declaration: SymSparseCSC extends x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSC.
    Symmetric sparse matrix is derived from SparseCSC matrix. All sparse data is
stored in CSC format, (same as symmetric dense).

    
Results of some cell-wise operations on symmetric matrix is stored in dense instances.
